      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but shows noticeable wear both inside and out. Expect some cosmetic blemishes on the exterior, worn interior surfaces, and likely some minor mechanical issues that may need attention. It's a functional vehicle suitable for a buyer who doesn't mind putting some work into it.",
